data.description: Welcome to Your Lake Wanda Ranch Retreat w/ Seasonal Lake Views! This single-floor living home offers the perfect blend of comfort, luxury touches, and nature's beauty. Upon entry, you'll be captivated by the spaciousness & charm. The deluxe kitchen boasts an abundance of cabinets and granite countertops, perfect for both entertainers and chefs. High ceilings with exposed beams and hardwood floors create a spacious and inviting atmosphere. The primary bedroom, with an en-suite bathroom, offers a private feel. All bedrooms are generously sized. Ductless split systems ensure year-round comfort with AC & Heat, with wood and pellet stoves for coziness. A sturdy metal roof adds durability & a great aesthetic look. A bonus room suits your needs, whether it's a second living room, family room, or office. Level corner lot, fenced in backyard, two driveways, a shed, and an oversized deck. Located minutes from Mountain Creek, Warwick's amenities, lake, parks, fishing, boating, and a huge state park, your dream lifestyle awaits. Please note, there used to be a bath tub in the primary bathroom, so water hook up and drain still there. Seller in process of fixing back fence corner and other items around the home. Property is Lake Wanda NOT Highland Lakes (no HOA fee).
